- You know what would teach him a lesson?

19:26.865 --> 19:28.866
If he saw me and you
making, out.

19:28.867 --> 19:31.102
I don, know.
He's not even looking.

19:31.103 --> 19:33.304
- Excellent.
- Stan Smith!

19:33.305 --> 19:35.473
We found your
food graveyard.

19:35.474 --> 19:37.942
You haven, been getting better at all.

19:37.943 --> 19:40.943
