19:43.081 --> 19:46.017
Guys, I can explain.
I was lying to you.

19:46.018 --> 19:48.419
Debbie was the best thing
that ever happened to me...

19:48.420 --> 19:51.420
and you drove her away because of your
stupid obsession with how people look.

19:51.823 --> 19:54.823
I had a real connection with someone
for the first time in my life...

19:54.993 --> 19:57.261
and all you cared about
was her appearance.

19:57.262 --> 19:59.697
