20:16.648 --> 20:19.648
- I like you so much, Steve.
- Oh, I love your chunky lips.

20:19.718 --> 20:22.718
No!

20:23.155 --> 20:25.156
Uh, hi.
Still waiting for bread sticks.

20:25.157 --> 20:28.157
