I don, know if this is your station.

20:29.695 --> 20:32.695
They're so...
happy together.

20:33.131 --> 20:36.131
Steve's right.
It's me that's been ugly.

20:36.168 --> 20:39.168
Inside... and outside.

20:39.771 --> 20:42.740
