20:47.980 --> 20:50.980
Bro! Bro! Bro! Bro!

20:54.686 --> 20:57.686
Steve, whether you wanna date a fatso,
a girl with hairy arms...

20:57.789 --> 20:59.857
or even one with
Kirsten Dunst teeth...

